 come now to the Adjournment.     Share         Adjournment       Resolved, That this House do now adjourn .—( James Morris .)           4.04 pm          H ouse adjourned.                     ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright          